dct:title.value: EFFECTS OF ALUMINUM ON SEED GERMINATION AND INITIAL GROWTH OF PHYSIC NUT SEEDLINGS

bibo:abstract.value: Aluminum toxicity is one of the major factors that limit plant  growth and crop yield in acid soils.  The phytotoxic effects of aluminum on seed germination and initial growth of physic nut seedlings were investigated in the present study.
